# REST Client Test File for Polls Endpoint
# This file uses the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Test 1: Get first 10 polls (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls
Accept: application/json

### Test 2: Get first 5 polls with explicit parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=0&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### Test 3: Get next 5 polls (skip first 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=5&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### Test 4: Get polls with larger page size
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=0&limit=20
Accept: application/json

### Test 5: Get polls from middle page
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=10&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Test 6: Test with skip=0, limit=1 (minimal response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=0&limit=1
Accept: application/json

### Test 7: Test with high skip value (should return empty if no polls)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=1000&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Test 8: Test without any parameters (should use defaults)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls
Accept: application/json

### Test 9: Test with limit=0 (edge case)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=0&limit=0
Accept: application/json

### Test 10: Test with negative values (edge case)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls?skip=-1&limit=-1
Accept: application/json